{"id":"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06","title":"第 6 课 - 将属性绑定添加到组件的模板中","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"lesson-6---add-a-property-binding-to-a-components-template\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5tok8peuoipjsdqs604oi7bre\">第 6 课 - 将属性绑定添加到组件的模板中<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-6---add-a-property-binding-to-a-components-template\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1bi4dja9y52w3pgdgzkvauh4\">这节课演示了如何将属性绑定添加到模板中并通过它将动态数据传给组件。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9b0304m4wmxslkazn9h6yr4kn\"><strong>预计时间</strong>: 约10分钟</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dgz18b1gp73zvopex0v1fcu78\"><strong>初始代码：</strong> \n<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-05\"></live-example></p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6eb7ol4goa0dw5rcygbm2eaq5\"><strong>完成的代码：</strong> \n<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-06\"></live-example></p>\n<h2 id=\"what-youll-learn\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cy8qhuh22qozu5okjmjfdf3nx\">你将学到<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#what-youll-learn\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"hb3f1a7cs49x357b4qn3o2at\">应用程序在 <code>HomeComponent</code> 模板中具有一些数据绑定。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dzyghfiutwkjhk91e379ifhs7\">应用程序将数据从 <code>HomeComponent</code> 发送到 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"conceptual-preview-of-inputs\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eeam3k169tsbsub1gv24k6e72\">输入属性的概念性预览<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#conceptual-preview-of-inputs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"aw3awzx00gdyur25b3gju1j2o\">在这一课中，你将继续通过使用属性绑定将数据从父组件传递到子组件的过程。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4lghd5e7siy7i8cmryxgc0qiv\">属性绑定能让你将变量连接到 Angular 模板中的 <code><a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code> 属性。然后把数据动态绑定到此 <code><a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code>。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dxa46w6z9s16ek7jb2wney2sr\">更深入的解释，请参阅<a href=\"guide/property-binding\">属性绑定</a>指南。</p>\n<h2 id=\"step-1---update--tag-in-the-homecomponent-template\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bow9yqp00mt84okjkgtxjwcku\">第 1 步 - 更新 <code>HomeComponent</code> 模板中的 <code>&lt;app-housing-location&gt;</code> 标记<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#step-1---update--tag-in-the-homecomponent-template\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1co0ezx9zodfr71l3l9n31w6s\">此步骤将属性绑定添加到 <code>&lt;app-housing-location&gt;</code> 标记上。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eug3k0hymd4usfrh9oohvkiee\">在代码编辑器中：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7oiouk36c6xv3lsj2yevl8hzt\">导航到 <code>src/app/home/home.component.ts</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8vhetk7bgj56zb7tobaa08xv5\">在\n<code>@Component</code>装饰器的模板属性中，更新代码以匹配下面的代码： \n<code-example header=\"添加 housingLocation 属性绑定\" path=\"first-app-lesson-06/src/app/home/home.component.ts\" region=\"add-property-binding\">\n  &lt;app-housing-location [housingLocation]=\"housingLocation\"&gt;&lt;/app-housing-location&gt; \n</code-example></p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d2m71m2cimnbddqkmzwhizq4n\">当向组件标签添加属性绑定时，我们使用 <code>[attribute] = \"value\"</code> 语法来通知 Angular 所赋的值应该视为来自组件类的属性，而不是字符串值。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4xabje76xjfwxq3d9cb9lywht\">右侧的值是 <code>HomeComponent</code> 中的属性名称。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"step-2---confirm-the-code-still-works\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7avbwxoudcvi6smeq5i1zg8qf\">第 2 步 - 确认代码仍然能工作<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#step-2---confirm-the-code-still-works\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6a1306fc3w56aeqm1wcmz5ewr\">保存你的更改并确认应用程序没有任何错误。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2kcshog2nszydh73ast6suqu6\">在继续下一步之前更正所有错误。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"lesson-review\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ckmo8mg671uh3oxv2z72tuj64\">课程回顾<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-review\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1nrij82mf5ursr25ocx71nplo\">在这节课中，你添加了一个新的属性绑定，并传入了对类属性的引用。现在，<code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 就能访问可用来在自定义组件中显示的数据了。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2vi4aou9du2w1ijyabax7x8qx\">如果你在学习这节课时遇到了任何问题，可以在<live-example></live-example>查看完整代码。</p>\n<h2 id=\"next-steps\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c4pkljueu68ifjoi5994e9l8o\">下一步<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#next-steps\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3kv1kmippfmze690ajdhygxcp\"><a href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07\">第 7 课 - 向组件模板添加插值</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ep5mlw3d5q1ucm62jzem9a7pc\">有关这节课中涵盖的主题的更多信息，请访问：<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"mfyxx87fibqbnu58gbuv5vkk\"><a href=\"guide/property-binding\">属性绑定</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间：Tue Jul 11 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Input\n - guide/property-binding\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#conceptual-preview-of-inputs\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-6---add-a-property-binding-to-a-components-template\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-review\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#next-steps\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#step-1---update--tag-in-the-homecomponent-template\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#step-2---confirm-the-code-still-works\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#what-youll-learn\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07\n-->"}